{
  "video_id": "4ZB29iq_Zd8",
  "title": "Christina Warinner: Tracking ancient diseases using ... plaque",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15260.0,
      "end_time": 17259.0,
      "text": "Have you ever wondered"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17260.0,
      "end_time": 20260.0,
      "text": "what is inside your dental plaque?"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20260.0,
      "end_time": 22260.0,
      "text": "Probably not, but people like me do."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22260.0,
      "end_time": 24260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m an archeological geneticist"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24260.0,
      "end_time": 26260.0,
      "text": "at the Center for Evolutionary Medicine"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26260.0,
      "end_time": 28260.0,
      "text": "at the University of Zurich,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28260.0,
      "end_time": 31260.0,
      "text": "and I study the origins and evolution of human health and disease"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31260.0,
      "end_time": 33260.0,
      "text": "by conducting genetic research"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 33260.0,
      "end_time": 36260.0,
      "text": "on the skeletal and mummified remains of ancient humans."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36260.0,
      "end_time": 39260.0,
      "text": "And through this work, I hope to better understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39260.0,
      "end_time": 41260.0,
      "text": "the evolutionary vulnerabilities of our bodies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 41260.0,
      "end_time": 44260.0,
      "text": "so that we can improve"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44260.0,
      "end_time": 46260.0,
      "text": "and better manage our health in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 46260.0,
      "end_time": 49260.0,
      "text": "There are different ways to approach evolutionary medicine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 49260.0,
      "end_time": 51260.0,
      "text": "and one way is to extract human DNA"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 51260.0,
      "end_time": 53260.0,
      "text": "from ancient bones."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 53260.0,
      "end_time": 55260.0,
      "text": "And from these extracts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 55260.0,
      "end_time": 58260.0,
      "text": "we can reconstruct the human genome at different points in time"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 58260.0,
      "end_time": 61260.0,
      "text": "and look for changes that might be related to adaptations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 61260.0,
      "end_time": 64259.0,
      "text": "risk factors and inherited diseases."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 64260.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67260.0,
      "text": "But this is only one half of the story."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 67260.0,
      "end_time": 70260.0,
      "text": "The most important health challenges today"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 70260.0,
      "end_time": 73260.0,
      "text": "are not caused by simple mutations in our genome,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 73260.0,
      "end_time": 76260.0,
      "text": "but rather result from a complex and dynamic interplay"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 76260.0,
      "end_time": 78260.0,
      "text": "between genetic variation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 78260.0,
      "end_time": 80260.0,
      "text": "diet, microbes and parasites"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 80260.0,
      "end_time": 82260.0,
      "text": "and our immune response."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 82260.0,
      "end_time": 84260.0,
      "text": "All of these diseases"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 84260.0,
      "end_time": 86260.0,
      "text": "have a strong evolutionary component"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 86260.0,
      "end_time": 88260.0,
      "text": "that directly relates to the fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 88260.0,
      "end_time": 90260.0,
      "text": "that we live today in a very different environment"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 90260.0,
      "end_time": 93260.0,
      "text": "than the ones in which our bodies evolved."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 93260.0,
      "end_time": 95260.0,
      "text": "And in order to understand these diseases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 95260.0,
      "end_time": 98260.0,
      "text": "we need to move past studies of the human genome alone"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 98260.0,
      "end_time": 100260.0,
      "text": "and towards a more holistic approach"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 100260.0,
      "end_time": 102260.0,
      "text": "to human health in the past."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 102260.0,
      "end_time": 104260.0,
      "text": "But there are a lot of challenges for this."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 104260.0,
      "end_time": 107260.0,
      "text": "And first of all, what do we even study?"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 107260.0,
      "end_time": 110260.0,
      "text": "Skeletons are ubiquitous; they&#39;re found all over the place."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 110260.0,
      "end_time": 113260.0,
      "text": "But of course, all of the soft tissue has decomposed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 113260.0,
      "end_time": 115260.0,
      "text": "and the skeleton itself"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 115260.0,
      "end_time": 117260.0,
      "text": "has limited health information."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 117260.0,
      "end_time": 119260.0,
      "text": "Mummies are a great source of information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 119260.0,
      "end_time": 122260.0,
      "text": "except that they&#39;re really geographically limited"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 122260.0,
      "end_time": 124260.0,
      "text": "and limited in time as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 124260.0,
      "end_time": 127260.0,
      "text": "Coprolites are fossilized human feces,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 127260.0,
      "end_time": 129259.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re actually extremely interesting."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 129258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 132260.0,
      "text": "You can learn a lot about ancient diet and intestinal disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 132260.0,
      "end_time": 134260.0,
      "text": "but they are very rare."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 134260.0,
      "end_time": 137260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 137260.0,
      "end_time": 139260.0,
      "text": "So to address this problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 139260.0,
      "end_time": 141260.0,
      "text": "I put together a team of international researchers"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 141260.0,
      "end_time": 143260.0,
      "text": "in Switzerland, Denmark and the U.K."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 143260.0,
      "end_time": 149260.0,
      "text": "to study a very poorly studied, little known material"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 149260.0,
      "end_time": 151260.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s found on people everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 151260.0,
      "end_time": 154260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a type of fossilized dental plaque"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 154260.0,
      "end_time": 157260.0,
      "text": "that is called officially dental calculus."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 157260.0,
      "end_time": 159260.0,
      "text": "Many of you may know it by the term tartar."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 159260.0,
      "end_time": 161260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s what the dentist cleans off your teeth"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 161260.0,
      "end_time": 163260.0,
      "text": "every time that you go in for a visit."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 163260.0,
      "end_time": 165260.0,
      "text": "And in a typical dentistry visit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 165260.0,
      "end_time": 168260.0,
      "text": "you may have about 15 to 30 milligrams removed."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 168260.0,
      "end_time": 171260.0,
      "text": "But in ancient times before tooth brushing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 171260.0,
      "end_time": 174260.0,
      "text": "up to 600 milligrams might have built up on the teeth"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 174260.0,
      "end_time": 176260.0,
      "text": "over a lifetime."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 176260.0,
      "end_time": 179260.0,
      "text": "And what&#39;s really important about dental calculus"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 179260.0,
      "end_time": 182260.0,
      "text": "is that it fossilizes just like the rest of the skeleton,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 182260.0,
      "end_time": 185260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s abundant in quantity before the present day"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 185260.0,
      "end_time": 187260.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s ubiquitous worldwide."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 187260.0,
      "end_time": 190260.0,
      "text": "We find it in every population around the world at all time periods"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 190260.0,
      "end_time": 192260.0,
      "text": "going back tens of thousands of years."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 192260.0,
      "end_time": 195260.0,
      "text": "And we even find it in neanderthals and animals."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 195260.0,
      "end_time": 197260.0,
      "text": "And so previous studies"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 197260.0,
      "end_time": 199260.0,
      "text": "had only focused on microscopy."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 199260.0,
      "end_time": 201260.0,
      "text": "They&#39;d looked at dental calculus under a microscope,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 201260.0,
      "end_time": 204260.0,
      "text": "and what they had found was things like pollen"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 204260.0,
      "end_time": 206260.0,
      "text": "and plant starches,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 206260.0,
      "end_time": 208260.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;d found muscle cells from animal meats"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 208260.0,
      "end_time": 210260.0,
      "text": "and bacteria."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 210260.0,
      "end_time": 213260.0,
      "text": "And so what my team of researchers, what we wanted to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 213260.0,
      "end_time": 215260.0,
      "text": "is say, can we apply"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 215260.0,
      "end_time": 217260.0,
      "text": "genetic and proteomic technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 217260.0,
      "end_time": 219260.0,
      "text": "to go after DNA and proteins,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 219260.0,
      "end_time": 222260.0,
      "text": "and from this can we get better taxonomic resolution"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 222260.0,
      "end_time": 224260.0,
      "text": "to really understand what&#39;s going on?"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 224260.0,
      "end_time": 226260.0,
      "text": "And what we found"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 226260.0,
      "end_time": 228260.0,
      "text": "is that we can find many commensal and pathogenic bacteria"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 228260.0,
      "end_time": 231260.0,
      "text": "that inhabited the nasal passages and mouth."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 231260.0,
      "end_time": 234260.0,
      "text": "We also have found immune proteins"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 234260.0,
      "end_time": 237260.0,
      "text": "related to infection and inflammation"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 237260.0,
      "end_time": 240260.0,
      "text": "and proteins and DNA related to diet."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 240260.0,
      "end_time": 243260.0,
      "text": "But what was surprising to us, and also quite exciting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 243260.0,
      "end_time": 245260.0,
      "text": "is we also found bacteria"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 245260.0,
      "end_time": 247260.0,
      "text": "that normally inhabit upper respiratory systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 247260.0,
      "end_time": 250260.0,
      "text": "So it gives us virtual access to the lungs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 250260.0,
      "end_time": 253260.0,
      "text": "which is where many important diseases reside."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 253260.0,
      "end_time": 255260.0,
      "text": "And we also found bacteria"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 255260.0,
      "end_time": 257260.0,
      "text": "that normally inhabit the gut."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 257260.0,
      "end_time": 260260.0,
      "text": "And so we can also now virtually gain access"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 260260.0,
      "end_time": 262260.0,
      "text": "to this even more distant organ system"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 262260.0,
      "end_time": 264260.0,
      "text": "that, from the skeleton alone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 264260.0,
      "end_time": 266260.0,
      "text": "has long decomposed."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 266260.0,
      "end_time": 268260.0,
      "text": "And so by applying ancient DNA sequencing"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 268260.0,
      "end_time": 270260.0,
      "text": "and protein mass spectrometry technologies"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 270260.0,
      "end_time": 272260.0,
      "text": "to ancient dental calculus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 272260.0,
      "end_time": 275260.0,
      "text": "we can generate immense quantities of data"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 275260.0,
      "end_time": 278260.0,
      "text": "that then we can use to begin to reconstruct a detailed picture"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 278260.0,
      "end_time": 280260.0,
      "text": "of the dynamic interplay"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 280260.0,
      "end_time": 282260.0,
      "text": "between diet, infection and immunity"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 282260.0,
      "end_time": 284260.0,
      "text": "thousands of years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 284260.0,
      "end_time": 286260.0,
      "text": "So what started out as an idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 286260.0,
      "end_time": 288260.0,
      "text": "is now being implemented"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 288260.0,
      "end_time": 290260.0,
      "text": "to churn out millions of sequences"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 290260.0,
      "end_time": 292260.0,
      "text": "that we can use to investigate"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 292260.0,
      "end_time": 295260.0,
      "text": "the long-term evolutionary history of human health and disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 295260.0,
      "end_time": 298260.0,
      "text": "right down to the genetic code of individual pathogens."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 298260.0,
      "end_time": 300260.0,
      "text": "And from this information"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 300260.0,
      "end_time": 302260.0,
      "text": "we can learn about how pathogens evolve"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 302260.0,
      "end_time": 305260.0,
      "text": "and also why they continue to make us sick."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 305260.0,
      "end_time": 307260.0,
      "text": "And I hope I have convinced you"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 307260.0,
      "end_time": 309260.0,
      "text": "of the value of dental calculus."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 309260.0,
      "end_time": 311260.0,
      "text": "And as a final parting thought,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 311260.0,
      "end_time": 314260.0,
      "text": "on behalf of future archeologists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 314260.0,
      "end_time": 317260.0,
      "text": "I would like to ask you to please think twice"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 317260.0,
      "end_time": 319260.0,
      "text": "before you go home and brush your teeth."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 319260.0,
      "end_time": 321260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 321260.0,
      "end_time": 323260.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 323260.0,
      "end_time": 325260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}